In a large bowl, whisk the buttermilk, 2 tablespoons (25 mL) white wine vinegar, oil, mustard, and 1 teaspoon (5 mL) pepper. Add the pasta and toss. Add broccoli, carrots, asparagus, and peas. Toss in shrimp, olives, dill, and scallions. Cover; refrigerate until serving time. Place the kale in a large bowl. Add the tomatoes, red wine vinegar, and pepper. Toss well. Serve with the shrimp mixture.